          }
          text: "## Indriya Went From Zero To 50M+ Views In A Year. Here\'s How.\n[Repositioning of Skybags from a bag to Adventure Identity](https://www.schbang.com/casestudies/repositioning-of-skybags-from-a-bag-to-adventure-identity)\n\n## Repositioning of Skybags from a bag to Adventure Identity\n[How we work](https://www.schbang.com/about-us)\n[Our Partnerships](https://www.schbang.com/our-partnerships)\n[News Centre](https://www.schbang.com/news-centre)\n[Schbang Network](https://www.schbang.com/schbang-network)\n[CSR](https://www.schbang.com/csr)\n[Meet the team](https://www.schbang.com/team)\n[Making Headlines with our omnichannel launch campaign for a bold original News Show](https://www.schbang.com/casestudies/omnichannel-launch-for-vantage-point)\n\n## Making Headlines with our omnichannel launch campaign for a bold original News Show\n[Hyper-personalized social campaign for India\342\200\231s biggest food delivery startup](https://www.schbang.com/casestudies/khali-ka-khaali-kart-with-swiggy-instamart)\n\n## Hyper-personalized social campaign for India\342\200\231s biggest food delivery startup\n[Blogs](https://www.schbang.com/blogs)\n[the Edge](https://www.schbang.com/the-edge)\n[The MarTech Audit Every CMO Should Run Before Q3](https://www.schbang.com/post/the-martech-audit-every-cmo-should-run-before-q3)\n\n## The MarTech Audit Every CMO Should Run Before Q3\n[Month In A Nutshell April Edition](https://www.schbang.com/post/month-in-a-nutshell)\n\n## Month In A Nutshell April Edition\n[Careers](https://www.schbang.com/careers)\n[Contact\302\240us\302\240\302\240\342\206\222](https://www.schbang.com/contact-us)"
