            text: "BrighterThanEver Film for a Global Fashion Brand"
          }
          text: "# We\'re on a mission to take the very best of Indian creative talent to the world. Driven by a ferocious hunger to create tangible impact for your business, we work with in-house specialists, industry partners and technology leaders to push the boundaries of creativity and put your brand on the global stage.\n[Dive into our culture \302\240\342\206\222](https://www.schbang.com/about-us)\n\n#### What defines us\n\n# We\'re on a mission to take the very best of Indian creative talent to the world. Driven by a ferocious hunger to create tangible impact for your business, we work with in-house specialists, industry partners and technology leaders to push the boundaries of creativity and put your brand on the global stage.\n[Dive into our culture \302\240\342\206\222](https://www.schbang.com/about-us)\n[Dive into our Culture](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[Dive into our Culture](https://www.schbang.com/about-us)\n[Gamified web experience for India\'s favourite candy brandCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor TextCursor Text\n\n[no-click] {pointer-events: none;}\n\n[children-selectable] * {pointer-events: auto;}\n\n\n.text-link:hover {\n\tcolor: var(--dark-color);\n}\n.text-link:hover .text-link_line {\n\theight: 100%;\n}\n\n.join-us_visual-item {opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;}\n.join-us_visual-item.active {opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto;}\n\n\n.animated-text {\n  width: 200px; /* Adjust width as needed */\n  height: 40px; /* Adjust height as needed */\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.text {\n  display: inline-block;\n  animation: scroll-text 5s linear infinite !important;\n  animation-fill-mode: both;\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n\n@keyframes scroll-text {\n  0% {\n    transform: translateX(100%);\n  }\n  100% {\n    transform: translateX(-150%);\n  }\n}](https://www.schbang.com/casestudies/creating-a-zesty-gamified-website-for-a-popular-candy-brand)\nGamified web experience for India\'s favourite candy brand\nC