          text: "# Trending now\n[The MarTech Audit Every CMO Should Run Before Q3 5 minBlog Post5 minRead Now](https://www.schbang.com/post/the-martech-audit-every-cmo-should-run-before-q3)\n[Month In A Nutshell April Edition10 MinsBlog10 MinsRead Now](https://www.schbang.com/post/month-in-a-nutshell)\n[The Content-SEO Loop: Building Stories That Also Rank With AI Acceleration5 minBlog5 minRead Now](https://www.schbang.com/post/the-content-seo-loop-building-stories-that-also-rank-with-ai-acceleration)\n\n# Awards..\n[2022Reinforcement LearningEditorial, 3D Renders\342\206\263 Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/photos/pRuLk09dyho)\n[2021AI systems learns from their own experiences3D Renders\342\206\263 Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/photos/trP-snuj5dI)\n[2022Applications of AIEditorial, 3D Renders\342\206\263 Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/photos/6R1rq5yTl7g)\n\n# Just went live with:\n[The Ultimate Feed for Fevicol](https://schbang1.webflow.io/casestudys/the-ultimate-feed-for-fevicol)\n[Brighter Than Ever Film for H&M](https://schbang1.webflow.io/casestudys/brighter-than-ever-film-for-h-m)\n[Tailored Website Experiences for Tata Communications users](https://schbang1.webflow.io/casestudys/tata-communications-website)"
