          headers {
            type: MARKDOWN_NODE_TYPE_HEADER_3
            text: "Shopify Partner"
          }
          text: "### Sammies by Social Samosa - Best use of social media for a cause (Gold)\nFor Myntra (#MyntraForPride Campaign)\n2023\n\n### Digies by Afaqs! - Best content Marketing (Gold)\nFor Brittania\n2023\n\n### Independent agency of the year\n2023\n\n### Kyoorious - Real-time Response\nFor Fevicol (Ronaldo topical)\n2022\n\n### Shorty Awards - Public Health\nFor J&J (#BeThechange for TB)\n2023\n\n### Abby - Innovative use of Mobile (Gold)\nFor Amazon Prime Video\n2022\n[\342\206\222](https://www.schbang.com/)\nWhen Schbang presented the concept and storyboard to Sony Music and us, they brought a rich visual language to our song and we knew, immediately, that they were the right partners for Roz Roz.\n\n#### The Yellow Diary Team\nIndia is a key market for our growth agenda and investing in building the Date Crown brand is key to the long-term success of this agenda. Our partnership with Schbang has been a great stepping stone in building a strong Date Crown brand.\n\n#### Paul O\342\200\231Neill,Vice President Marketing,Date Crown\nFevicol has over the years come to epitomize strong bonds. The Friendship Day campaign with Schbang provided us with an apt opportunity to bring alive this proposition; fantastic to see such a wide array of brands interact with Fevicol through this medium!\n\n#### Giridhar Seetharam, Chief Business Officer,\302\240Fevicol\nThe campaign #MoodHiBadalDiya for Tata Neu has received a wonderful response from our social community. This campaign has seen excellent effort from every single one of the team members involved behind the scenes. Thank you for being part of this journey Schbang!\n\n#### Isha ShroffAssociate Director, Social MediaTata Neu\n\n### ONDC Partner\nComplete e-commerce solutions to meet your business goals.\n\n### Google Premier Partner\nLeverage the power of Google Ads to scale your business.\n\n### Zoho Premium Partner\nDesign and implement integrated business architectures and digital transformation solutions.\n\n### MoEngage Partner\nLeverage the marketing automation platform to boost customer engagement and retention.\n\n### Adobe Solution Partner\nDevelop sophisticated and personalised solutions for enterprises with deeper consumer understanding and built-in analytics.\n\n### Node.js\nBuilding & deploy web apps, APIs, and other software solutions with scalability & high performance at the core.\n\n### Shopify Partner\nBuild robust and effective online stores with the leading e-commerce platform.\n[\342\206\222](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[India: 1234Contact Us](https://www.schbang.com/contact-us)\n[London: 1234Contact Us](https://www.schbang.com/contact-us)\n[Amsterdam: 1234Contact Us](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[MU](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[BLR](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[DL](https://www.schbang.com/)\n[LDN](https://www.schbang.com/)"
        }
