  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Verifying Design Consistency**\n\nI\'ve got the build running now! I\'m comparing the aesthetic and copy to the requested example, making sure \"Brand Brick Studio\" copy is integrated as directed. I\'m starting by reviewing the `Hero` section to ensure consistency with Schbang\'s design.\n\n\n**Refining Aesthetic Choices**\n\nI\'ve nailed the initial design direction! I\342\200\231ve integrated the requested `motion` library, large typography with Space Grotesk and Inter fonts, and elegant Tailwind CSS classes to establish a dark theme. I\'ve focused on ensuring the visual style mirrors Schbang\'s, achieving that bold and clean aesthetic. I\342\200\231ve ensured the landing page\'s overall style is consistent with high-end agency sites. The components are broken down to match the copy deck exactly.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the full landing page for **Brand Brick Studio** exactly according to the copy deck you provided, structuring all sections to mirror a highly polished, professional agency website.\n\nHere is an overview of the implementation:\n- **Premium Dark Aesthetics:** Inspired by top-tier agency designs, I applied a sleek, high-contrast dark theme spanning from the sticky navigation down to the footer. \n- **Bold Typography & Motion:** I integrated \"Space Grotesk\" for large, blocky, attention-demanding display headings and \"Inter\" for readable body text. Smooth staggered entrance animations were added across the fold to replicate that premium agency feel.\n- **Section-by-Section Accuracy:**\n  - **Hero & Top Strip:** Immediate impact with your main value propositions.\n  - **Manifesto & What Defines Us:** A bold typography-led section featuring a seamless infinite scrolling text marquee.\n  - **Capabilities & Services:** Styled as clean, structured, responsive grids for easy reading and visual breathing room.\n  - **Packages, Proof, Stack, & Experience:** Modular bento-grid and card layouts styled carefully to handle all the exact pricing, stats, tool stacks, and quote information you provided.\n  - **Contact Footer:** A loud, confident call-to-action block integrating all location, social, and direct contact details clearly.\n\nThe website is fully built using React with TypeScript and is available in the live preview."
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 102761591
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
